N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 367.7 - Disposition

State Regulations

Unless precluded by statute, disposition may be made of any
adjudicatory proceeding by stipulation, agreed settlement, consent order, default or other informal method, provided that nothing herein shall be
construed to require any such disposition. Notes
